<h1 class="headline-title">13 岁少女肢解同窗好友，也许我们都小看她了</h1>


<span class="img-source">图片：Yestone 邑石网正版图库</span>


<img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9b704e39dc83ae7202fefc8d192e10f3.jpg" alt="">
